      <sec>
        <title>3-Methyl-thiazolo[3,2-a]benzimidazolium iodide (<bold>2a</bold>)</title>
        <p><sup>1</sup>H-NMR (CD<sub>3</sub>OD, 300 MHz): <italic>&#x3B4;</italic> = 2.92 (d, 3H, CH<sub>3</sub>, J = 1.2), 7.26 (q, 1H, =CH, J = 1.2), 7.55-7.75 (m, 2H, Ar) , 7.80-7.90 (m, 1H, Ar) , 8.15-8.25 (m, 1H, Ar); <sup>13</sup>C-NMR (CD<sub>3</sub>OD, 75 MHz): <italic>&#x3B4;</italic> = 14.21, 112.02, 114.37, 115.50, 125.58, 128.03, 129.20, 134.32, 138.14, 155.85.</p>
      </sec>
